Functional Data Engineering.
A set of best practices.

Apacheflow - it is a work flow engine that helps you author, schedule and monitor your data pipelines
Inspired by facebooks data swarm. 

functional programming - based on object oriented programming. A subset of it.
In functional code, the output value of the function depends only on the arguments that are passed to the functions so 
calling the funciton twice with the same input will result in the same output.

Pure functions - in programming they are functions limited to their own scope. This brings clarity to the process. 
